SANTA will be visiting the Equinox Mall in St Francis Street, Jeffreys Bay this festive season.Young and old can have their photos taken with Santa from 10:00 to 15:00 from December 17 to 12:00 on December 24. Photos will be developed at the mall.Residents can furthermore have their photos printed on a T-shirt or mug from December 11 to December 24.Safe time and have your gifts wrap at the mall by Gen-Net Printing from December 11 to 24.There will furthermore be a post box where children can post their letters to Santa.Three children s wishes will come true on December 24.24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.